    closer: "Whether you are incorporating as an Oxford University Innovation spinout with Oxford Science Enterprises investment, at Harwell Campus, Oxford Science Park, Begbroke Science Park, Milton Park, or Oxford BioEscalator, or through Oxford Brookes University Enterprise, accountants in our Oxford network handle OUI licensing, OSE equity structuring, KIC documentation, R&D-intensive SME categorisation, and Harwell Enterprise Zone mapping together at formation. Submit your details below for Oxford-specialist matches."
